+ Release v1.2-p1

+ This adds the ftp daemon again.


+ Release v1.2

* Added a fallback/recovery boot-mode which resets the IP address to 192.168.1.10 and inhibits the user application from running when no Ethernet cable is plugged in while booting.
* Added SMB network filesystem mount ('smbmount') support.
* Added NTP time synchronization support either through DHCP or the 'ntpserver' U-Boot environment variable.
* Updated the image sensor driver to relax capture region (region of interest) requirements.


+ Release v1.1 indXcam

Add support for samba mounting.
